= Mixed List Nesting

== Two-level mixed nesting

* Unordered item 1
  . Nested ordered A
  . Nested ordered B
* Unordered item 2

== Three-level mixed nesting

* Level 1 A
  . Level 2 A
    ** Level 3 A
    ** Level 3 B
  . Level 2 B
* Level 1 B

== Five-level mixed nesting

* UL depth 1 item A
  . OL depth 2 item A
    ** UL depth 3 item A
      .. OL depth 4 item A
        *** UL depth 5 item A
        *** UL depth 5 item B
      .. OL depth 4 item B
    ** UL depth 3 item B
  . OL depth 2 item B
* UL depth 1 item B
